<h1>Help: IT Ticketing System</h1>
<p>This guide will help you navigate and use the Ticklr Ticketing System effectively.</p>

<hr />

<h2>Submitting a Ticket</h2>
<ol>
    <li>Log in to the ticket system.</li>
    <li>Select <strong>"Create a Ticket"</strong> from the dashboard.</li>
    <li>Fill in the required fields (Description, Category, and Priority).</li>
    <li>Click <strong>"Create"</strong> to submit the ticket.</li>
</ol>

<h2>Viewing Your Tickets</h2>
<ol>
    <li>Click on <strong>"View Past Tickets"</strong> from the dashboard.</li>
    <li>Select any ticket to view its status or edit if necessary.</li>
</ol>

<h2>Editing a Ticket</h2>
<ol>
    <li>From your ticket list, click the <strong>"Edit"</strong> button next to a ticket.</li>
    <li>Update the relevant fields and click <strong>"Save"</strong>.</li>
</ol>

<h2>Closing a Ticket</h2>
<ol>
    <li>Open the ticket that has been resolved.</li>
    <li>Check the <strong>"Is Completed"</strong> box and save the changes.</li>
</ol>

